sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User/Client
  participant IF as Interface API
  participant IFDB as Interface DB + Outbox
  participant EB as Event Bus (unspecified)
  participant CO as Coordination Service
  participant CODB as Coordination DB + Outbox
  participant IN as Integration Service
  participant EXT as External System (unspecified)
  participant GOV as Governance Service
  participant AUD as Audit Store

  U->>IF: POST /input_reports (Idempotency-Key)
  IF->>IFDB: Upsert InputReport + Outbox record (txn)
  IF-->>U: 202 Accepted (input_report_id)

  IFDB-->>EB: Publish CloudEvent: input_report.created

  par Coordination consumption
    EB-->>CO: input_report.created
    CO->>CODB: Idempotent-consume check + write OutputReport (txn)
    CODB-->>EB: Publish output_report.generated
    CO->>CODB: Write ServiceRequest + WorkOrder (txn)
    CODB-->>EB: Publish service_request.created + work_order.created
  and Governance auditing
    EB-->>GOV: input_report.created
    GOV->>AUD: Append audit record
    EB-->>GOV: work_order.created
    GOV->>AUD: Append audit record
    GOV->>GOV: Evaluate policy rules
    alt Policy violation
      GOV-->>EB: policy.violation_detected (subject=work_order)
    end
  and Integration side effects
    EB-->>IN: work_order.created
    alt Side-effect required
      IN->>EXT: Create/update external record (retry/backoff + breaker)
      alt Success
        IN-->>EB: integration.completed (correlates to work_order)
      else Failure
        IN-->>EB: integration.failed (correlates to work_order)
      end
    else No side-effect
      IN-->>IN: No action
    end
  end

  EB-->>CO: integration.completed
  CO->>CODB: Update WorkOrder fields (txn) + Outbox
  CODB-->>EB: work_order.status_changed

  EB-->>GOV: work_order.status_changed
  GOV->>AUD: Append audit record